axioms nke puru omume: Atụmatụ ntọala na tiori puru omume
puru omume: Ihe puru omume nke mmemme nyere na ihe omume ọzọ emela
mgbanwe mgbanwe: Ngbanwe nke ụkpụrụ ya nwere ike ịbụ nsonaazụ ọnụọgụgụ nke ihe na-enweghị usoro
iche iche: Atụmanya nke ngbanwe squared nke mgbanwe na-enweghị usoro site n'ọnụ ya
ihe omume dabere: Ihe omume abụọ na-adabere ma ọ bụrụ na ihe omume nke otu na-emetụta ihe gbasara omume nke ọzọ
o yikar\u1ecbr\u1ecb ka \u1ecd ga-esi na: Nsonaazụ nwere otu ihe nwere ike ime
\u1ecdk\u1ecdl\u1ecdt\u1ecd deviation: Ntụnye nke ọnụọgụ mgbanwe ma ọ bụ mgbasasị nke otu ụkpụrụ
\u1ecdn\u1ee5 \u1ecdg\u1ee5g\u1ee5: Otu ihe njiri mara ụfọdụ ihe atụ
